OL,3,C'An insult': Sean Brown's family on
OL,4,CGovernment taking legal action
OL,6,FSiobhan said: "My father was an
OL,7,Finnocent victim in all of this, he
OL,8,Fdidn't deserve to die.
OL,10,F"He was just going about his normal
OL,11,Fday-today business."
OL,13,FSiobhan added: "We believe it's an
OL,14,Finsult to us as a family but also to
OL,15,Fthe memory of my father."
OL,17,FIn March a coroner called for a public
OL,18,Finquiry into the murder of Sean Brown
OL,19,Fafter ruling the case could not
OL,20,Fproceed due to the withholding of
OL,21,Fsensitive files.
