OL,4,CGovernment taking legal action
OL,6,FMr Justice Kinney said his ability to
OL,7,Fexamine the death had been
OL,8,F"compromised" by the extent of
OL,9,Fconfidential state material being
OL,10,Fexcluded from the proceedings on
OL,11,Fnational security grounds.
OL,13,FHe called on Northern Ireland
OL,14,FSecretary Chris Heaton-Harris to
OL,15,Festablish a public inquiry - with the
OL,16,Fdeadline passing this week.
