OL,3,C'An insult': Sean Brown's family on
OL,4,CGovernment taking legal action
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said they
OL,7,Fwere applying for leave to take a
OL,8,Fjudicial review relating to the
OL,9,Finquest. They did not state the
OL,10,Freasons for the action.
OL,12,F"It would be inappropriate to comment
OL,13,Ffurther at this stage given the matter
OL,14,Fis now the subject of judicial
OL,15,Fconsideration," they added.
OL,17,FIt is understood, however, the nature
OL,18,Fof the action centres on the partial
OL,19,Frelease of sensitive information
OL,20,Fduring proceedings.
