OL,6,FSean Brown, 61, was abducted and
OL,7,Fkilled by loyalists as he locked the
OL,8,Fgates at Bellaghy Wolfe Tones Club in
OL,9,FCo Londonderry in May 1997. No one has
OL,10,Fbeen convicted of his murder.
OL,12,FThe inquest, which began in March 2023
OL,13,Fhas heard how a number of people
OL,14,Flinked to the killing were state
OL,15,Fagents.
